high_descs: Move to the dining table past the fridge on the right.
Pick up a loaf of bread from the table.
Move to the fridge to the left around the corner.
Put the bread in the fridge and close the door.
Move to the counter to the right of the sink.
Pick up the bread from the counter.
Move to the fridge across from the sink to the left.
Put the bread in the fridge and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put two loafs of bread in the fridge.

high_descs: advance to the shelf, turn left, and cross the room to the round table
take the loaf of bread from the center of the table
turn around, and cross the room to the refrigerator. Stop and face the refrigerator doors
open the refrigerator door, place the bread on the shelf next to the grey plate, and close the door.
turn around and cross the room to the sink, then turn right and go forward to the counter with the loaf of bread and cauldron
take the loaf of bread from the counter
turn right and return to in front of the refrigerator
open the refrigerator door, place the bread to the right of the other bread, and close the door
anns.task_desc: Place two loaves of bread into the refrigerator

high_descs: Go straight then turn left, then go straight and turn right at the table.
Pick up the bread from the table, in front of the plant.
Turn around and go to the fridge to your left.
Put the bread in the fridge.
Turn around, go straight, then turn right to the counter.
Pick up the bread on the counter, to the left of the pot.
Turn and go back to the fridge.
Put the bread in the fridge, next to the other bread.
anns.task_desc: Put the two loafs of bread in the fridge.

high_descs: Walk over to the wooden shelving unit, then hang a left and walk across the room to the round wooden table in the far corner of the room.
Pick up the loaf of bread that is closest to the metal spoon on the round wooden table.
Turn around and begin walking forward, then hang a left and walk over to the fridge.
Open the fridge door and place the loaf of bread inside on the shelf to the right of the grey plate then close the fridge door.
Turn around and begin walking to the sink, then hang a right and walk over to the loaf of bread on the counter.
Pick up the loaf of bread off of the counter.
Turn around and begin walking forward, then hang a left and walk up to the fridge.
Open the fridge door and place the loaf of bread inside to the right of the loaf that is already in there, then close the fridge door.
anns.task_desc: Move two loaves of bread into the fridge.

high_descs: Walk a few steps, turn left, cross the room, go to the table to the right.
Pick up the loaf a bread by the spoon.
Turn around, walk to the stool, turn left, walk to the refrigerator.
Put the bread next to the plate in the refrigerator.
Turn around, walk to the sink, turn right, walk to the counter.
Pick up the bread in front of the bowl.
Walk back to the refrigerator.
Place the bread to the right of the other loaf of bread.
anns.task_desc: Put two loaves of bread in the refrigerator.
